AWS Bedrock Multi-Agent Framework

Hi Team,

I wanted to share some exciting news from AWS. They've just announced the new Bedrock Multi-Agent Framework, which enables orchestration of multiple AI agents for complex workflows.

Key Features:
- Multi-agent orchestration with dynamic task allocation
- Built-in conversation memory and context management
- Integration with existing AWS services (Lambda, S3, DynamoDB)
- Support for custom agent definitions and tools

This could be really valuable for our platform's AI capabilities. The attached whitepaper has technical details, and you can read more on the AWS Bedrock Agents page (https://aws.amazon.com/bedrock/agents/).

Let's discuss this in our next AI/ML practice meeting.

Best regards,
Alice Anderson
CEO, Example Corp

